ccess-stories.jpg\" alt=\"\" />LOREM IPSUM IS SIMPLY TEXT</h1>\r\n<p>And typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>And typesetting</li>\r\n    <li>Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever</li>\r\n    <li>It has survived not only five</li>\r\n    <li>And typesetting industry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>',38),(82,'extended','','',38),(83,'body','','<div id=\"header-inner\"><img width=\"980\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Contact\" src=\"/images/headers/sitemap.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<p><r:snippet name=\"quick-navigation\"></r:snippet></p>\r\n<div id=\"inner_col-right\">\r\n<h1><img width=\"169\" height=\"312\" align=\"right\" src=\"/images/inner_photos/success-stories.jpg\" alt=\"\" />SITE MAP</h1>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"sidemenu\">\r\n <ul>\r\n   <r:find url=\"/\">\r\n     <r:snippet name=\"site-map\" />\r\n   </r:find>\r\n </ul>\r\n</div>',39),(84,'extended','','',39),(85,'body','Fckeditor','<div id=\"header-inner\"><img width=\"980\" height=\"96\" src=\"/images/headers/cooke-report.jpg\" alt=\"Contact\" /></div>\r\n<p><r:snippet name=\"quick-navigation\"></r:snippet></p>\r\n<div id=\"inner_col-right\">\r\n<h1><img width=\"169\" height=\"312\" align=\"right\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/inner_photos/success-stories.jpg\" />TRAINING WORKSHOPS</h1>\r\n<p>Gord Cooke offers comprehensive seminar and workshop-based training programs to help his clients learn to build and sell better homes. These programs range from a systems approach to building better homes to marketing and selling the key features and benefits of those homes once a company has achieved a high standard of building performance.</p>\r\n<p>These workshops and seminars are designed for anyone in the construction industry. Clients include home builders, as well as home builder&rsquo;s associations, manufacturers, architects and utilities who wish to provide training as a value added service to their customers.</p>\r\n<p>These customized training programs include :</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.buildingknowledge.com/training/CompBS.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Comprehensive Building Science Training</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.buildingknowledge.com/training/UnderstandingGreen.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Do You Want that in Green?</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.buildingknowledge.com/training/MktgandSelling.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Marketing and Selling the Better Built Home</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.buildingknowledge.com/training/MoistureRainMgmt.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Moisture and Rain Management </a></p>\r\n</div>',40),(86,'extended','','',40),(87,'body','Fckeditor','<div id=\"header-inner\"><img width=\"980\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Contact\" src=\"/images/headers/cooke-report.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<p><r:snippet name=\"quick-navigation\"></r:snippet></p>\r\n<div id=\"inner_col-right\">\r\n<h1><img width=\"169\" height=\"312\" align=\"right\" src=\"/images/inner_photos/success-stories.jpg\" alt=\"\" />SPONSORS</h1>\r\n<p>Gord&rsquo;s training programs are sponsored by a wide variety of building industry companies, organizations and associations. Consider working with your local association, HBA, utility, lumber yard or product distributor to sponsor a training program in your area. Please contact us to learn more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Gord Cooke Training Program Sponsors</strong></p>\r\n<p>Primary Sponsors<br />\r\nTO COME<br />\r\n[insert logos that link to each sponsor&rsquo;s website] TO COME</p>\r\n<p>Secondary Sponsors         <br />\r\nTO COME<br />\r\n[insert logos that link to each sponsor&rsquo;s website] TO COME</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>',41),(88,'extended','','',41);
